name: Airy Fairy - personalised gift for girls
description:
Personalised artwork for the nursery, bedroom or playroom

This wooden box frame (30x30x3.4cm) contains the name of the child spelt out with individual chipboard letters, which are handpainted according to the colour scheme. The craft papers lead the way with the design. Ribbons, trimmings and various embellishments are added to enhance this. Also included are printed extracts from nursery rhymes and the child's birth or christening details. A personal message from the sender and photos can also be included. 

Click on frame to enlarge.
